        {
            "id": 6011338,
            "title": "十大海外股票ETF績效比一比！半數收復關稅以來失土 00757漲逾8%最強",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普「解放日」揮動關稅大刀，全球股市應聲重挫，隨後川普態度急轉彎，給予關稅豁免期，恐慌心理逐漸收斂，台股站回 21000 點關卡。根據 CMoney 統計，自關稅政策宣布的前一個交易日迄今 (4/2~6/6)，市值前十大的海外股票原型 ETF 中，已有半數收復失土，包含統一 FANG+(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00757:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00757\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00757-TW</a>)、國泰<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00830:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00830\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00830-TW</a>)、國泰智能電動車 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00893:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00893\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00893-TW</a>)、復華 <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P500</a> 成長 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00924:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00924\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00924-TW</a>)、富邦 <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00662:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00662\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00662-TW</a>) 均已超車 4/2 的收盤價。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011338%2Fl%2Ffa390ce1293116ddc56cba09f0357f1d.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">十大海外股票ETF績效比一比！半數收復關稅以來失土 00757漲逾8%最強。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>比較 4/2~6/6 績效表現，00757 以超過 8% 的漲幅領先群雄，00830 以 5% 以上漲幅居次，00893 約上漲 1% 居第三。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>有別於硬體科技族群受到關稅政策雜音干擾，軟體族群因其數位服務特性，有望閃過關稅衝擊，成為全球資金避震抗波動的避風港。尤其生成式 AI 應用、雲端運算、資安及數位串流等產業等，具備長期發展潛力，營運持續增溫，吸引市場資金流入，表現相對抗跌，扮演重要穩盤力量。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其中，串流娛樂平台網飛 (Netflix)、雲端服務領先者微軟 (Microsoft) 的股價均在近期創下歷史新高紀錄，受到投資人高度關注。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>00757 配置的 10 家美國上市尖牙股中，便納入網飛 (Netflix)、微軟 (Microsoft) 與知名資安品牌 CrowdStrike 等軟體類佼佼者，有效發揮耐震助漲效果；同時涵蓋 AI 運算霸主輝達 (Nvidia)、晶片巨擘 (Broadcom) 等硬體大廠，多元布局於最具未來性、成長性及話題性的軟、硬體科技產業龍頭。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人指出，00757 採用「平均權重法」，不受市值大小所影響，讓所有成分股都能均衡貢獻其成長力道，廣泛參與各領域創新科技發展的商機，在這波關稅衝擊下展現韌性，並於反彈趨勢中釋放成長潛能，波段漲幅領先群雄。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
