        {
            "id": 6011511,
            "title": "〈熱門股〉jpp-KY營收創新猷 股價創近14個月新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>jpp-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5284:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5284\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5284-TW</a>)(經寶精密) 公布 5 月合併營收衝上 2.88 億元，月增 12.98%，年增 94.21%，再創新高紀錄，激勵本周股價漲近 20%，最高來到 186 元創去年 4 月中旬以來高。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011511%2Fl%2F1dca2206853f80b2a704caaeb8398cab.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">經寶5月營收創新高。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶表示，今年業績已較原預期的還要好，現在看來，還會再更好。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著客戶積極布建 AI 伺服器與資料中心，帶動經寶的通用型 AI 伺服器機櫃與通用型機殼、CDU 與冷熱分歧管等精密機構件等強勁出貨。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>經寶進一步說明，AI 伺服器訂單正持續湧入，並未受關稅措施明顯影響，產能擴充也同步進行中，第二座自動化噴烤漆廠第一季已投入建置中，預計最快明年初可量產，將有效緩解現有產線瓶頸。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>除了 AI 伺服器機櫃業務，經寶期許同步深耕航太版圖，6 月中旬將參加 2025 年法國巴黎航太展，拚爭取更多國際訂單。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-cnyeschart=\"cnyeschart\" src=\"https://so.cnyes.com/mobilechart/MobileChart.aspx?markettype=twstock&amp;charttype1=kchart&amp;stockcode=5284&amp;imgwidth=580&amp;imgheight=500&amp;bgcolor=2\"/>\n<figcaption>jpp-KY 日 K 線圖</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
